name: Pacman Rush
description:
Pacman Rush is a Score Oriented Game for Windows.
The main character is Straw Hat Pacman who must collect the score by eating foods
The player should get the highest score and should avoid the ghosts in the path.
you must press space for jump keep of the ghosts
If player hit the ghost, game over.
